# Uric Acid Tracker
A Progressive Web App for tracking uric acid levels.

## Quick Start
1. Open `index.html` in your browser
2. Or serve with a local web server:
   ```bash
   python -m http.server 8000
   ```

## Features
- Record daily uric acid values
- Support mg/dL and μmol/L units
- Historical trend charts
- Data export (CSV/JSON)
- Local storage (no server needed)
- PWA support (offline capable)
